dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2022, and includes the layers 'Waupaca_General_2022', and 'Waupaca_Shoreland_2022'. [General: Rural zoning districts for townships that fall under Waupaca County Zoning. Zoning data is tax parcel based.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://data2017-04-05t135915451z-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
